334
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:02,910
Damn, I was scared to death!

335
00:20:04,310 --> 00:20:05,350
You're still alive.

336
00:20:05,700 --> 00:20:06,580
Not for long.

337
00:20:06,780 --> 00:20:08,340
