356
00:21:28,150 --> 00:21:29,670
Okay, I'll put up with it.

357
00:21:30,350 --> 00:21:31,590
It was my fault.

358
00:21:33,590 --> 00:21:34,670
I don't know how to peel an apple.

359
00:21:34,910 --> 00:21:35,630
I'll peel an orange

360
00:21:35,630 --> 00:21:36,460
