548
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:19,810
♫ It’s like a habit♫

549
00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:21,030
I may not be able to give you what you want.

550
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:24,870
♫ I can be brave ♫

551
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:23,500
It's okay.

552
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:28,980
♫ I search in my memory ♫

553
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:27,830
I can fill it with my love.

554
00:35:28,980 --> 00:35:33,620
♫ In time, I find the answer ♫

555
00:35:34,030 --> 00:35:40,770
♫ I want to protect you ♫

556
00:35:36,990 --> 00:35:38,150
It's easy to be flipped,

557
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:40,100
but it's hard to announce love.

558
00:35:41,190 --> 00:35:45,200
♫ Love is short ♫

559
00:35:41,790 --> 00:35:42,590
So, Jiang Dian,

560
00:35:43,740 --> 00:35:45,140
give me a little more time, okay?

561
00:35:45,200 --> 00:35:48,860
♫ Even if I smile with regret ♫

562
00:35:48,990 --> 00:35:52,310
♫ It’s like a habit ♫

563
00:35:52,310 --> 00:35:57,090
♫ I can be brave ♫

564
00:35:57,090 --> 00:36:00,910
♫Smile and tear are all about you♫

